des: Music is not about genre or decade … music is about emotion. Radio.Bourbon is about the search for that emotion … finding those special artists with a unique viewpoint, and elegance and artistic style, and always searching for the perfect song. Our goal is to entertain and to explore the depths of the musical canon. But we also want to inform, and to educate, with shows that explore the human condition and dive deep into the magical and the metaphysical, striving to connect us to the ethos of the universe.
